---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — YT Downloader" description="Privacy policy for YT Downloader. We respect your privacy and do not track or store your downloads.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-24 w-full">
    <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:text-body prose-headings:text-ink max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-1.28px] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">At YT Downloader, we believe in minimal data collection. We do not require you to create an account, provide an email address, or share any personally identifiable information to use our service.</p>
      
      <p class="mb-4">When you use our website, we may collect standard server logs which include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Your IP address (temporarily for rate limiting and security)</li>
        <li>Browser type and version</li>
        <li>Time and date of your visit</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">The minimal information we do collect is used exclusively for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
        <li>Ensuring the technical stability and security of our platform</li>
        <li>Preventing abuse, spam, and DDoS attacks</li>
        <li>Understanding general usage patterns to improve our service</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Download History</h2>
      <p class="mb-4"><strong>We do not log, store, or track the URLs you download.</strong> Once a file is processed and delivered to you, the link between you and that file is immediately discarded from our active processing servers. Your downloads are your private business.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We use minimal cookies necessary for the website to function, such as remembering your dark mode/light mode preference. We do not use third-party tracking cookies or advertising cookies.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Our website interacts with third-party platforms (namely YouTube) to fetch the requested media. Please note that these third-party sites have their own privacy policies. We do not control and are not responsible for the privacy practices of any third-party services.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us via our <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
